des: Take a sniffy-sniff and start tasting with Gary Vaynerchuk and his friends from Wine Library. Wine shouldn't be intimidating, so what you'll find in this skill are awesome wine recommendations and approachable, straightforward tasting notes for some of Gary's favorite bottles, including many featured in his Monthly Wine Club. Enjoy tasting!
